              "content": "Takes a query and a list of text documents and returns them ordered by relevance with assigned relevance scores. It is recommended not to send more than 1000 documents in a single request. Long documents are automatically truncated to the value of max_tokens_per_doc. Structured data should be formatted as YAML strings for best performance.",
